abstract: The manufacturer warned consumers about Iams Veterinary Formula Feline Renal dry cat food in 5.5-pound bags.
snippet: The manufacturer warned consumers about Iams Veterinary Formula Feline Renal dry cat food in 5.5-pound bags.
lead_paragraph: The maker of Iams-brand products said it was recalling two lots of prescription cat food because of possible salmonella contamination.

headline.main: Prescription Cat Food Recalled Over Fears About Salmonella
headline.print_headline: Prescription Cat Food Recalled Over Fears About Salmonella
